      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·曹風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">候人.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼候人兮，何戈與祋。彼其之子，三百赤芾。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Those officers of escort
Have their carriers of lances and halberds.
But these creatures,
With their three hundred red covers for the knees ! —</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
