      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·曹風·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">候人.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維鵜在梁，不濡其翼。彼其之子，不稱其服。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The pelican is on the dam,
And will not wet his wings !
These creatures
Are not equal to their dress !</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
