      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·曹風·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">候人.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維鵜在梁，不濡其咮。彼其之子，不遂其媾。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The pelican is on the dam,
And will not wet his beak !
These creatures
Do not respond to the favour they enjoy.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
