      <prop type="x-translation-ref">候人.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>薈兮蔚兮，南山朝隮。婉兮孌兮，季女斯飢。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Extensive and luxuriant is the vegetation,
And up the south hill in the morning rise the vapours.
Tender is she and lovely,
But the young lady is suffering from hunger.</seg>
      </tuv>
